# Contains some utilities for interacting with the session service manually to join an isolate server running in IDE.

### Create Session

POST http://localhost:9127/v3/internal/session/aceb326f-da15-45bc-bf2f-11940c21780c
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "proxy": "devserver",
    "username": "notmattw",
    "ip": "127.0.0.1"
}
